To kick off 2025, we welcome @phoebe.litchfield to The Female Athlete Project. 

Tune in to learn about one of the biggest characters in the Australian women's cricket team and her take on the increasing responsibility of being a professional athlete.

Episode drops at 6AM AEDT Thursday 13.02. Subscribe via the link in @thefemaleathleteproject’s bio, or search ‘the female athlete project’ wherever you get your podcasts to listen as soon as it goes live. #womenssports
